name: The Revolution
description:
Ifreecans Collective The Revolution Tee.

Design: Kiboko Hachiyon

Sizes : S, M, L, 

Small 
34-36 inches - [86.4/91.4cm]
Medium
38/40 inches - [96.5/101cm]
Large
42/44 inches - [106.7/111.8cm]

100% ring spun cotton

Ifreecans Collective 2013 line featuring soft pastel shades tees with        ”Instant Vintage” print style.

The Print sinks directly into the fabric and print colours are mixed and selected to exclusively match the colour of the tee it will sit on, creating a vintage look and feel.

Each tee is screen printed by Ifreecans Collective in limited runs and are fitted, soft style ring spun cotton.

name: Mammy Can Do It
description:
Digital print by Kiboko Hachiyon.

*Printed on high quality 300gsm paper.
*Available in A3 [420 x 297 mm - 16.5 x 11.7 in].
*Click on image to zoom.

This print will be shipped in a reinforced round tube by Recorded Signed For (UK) , or by Standard Airmail £6 (elsewhere). For UK allow up to 5 working days for delivery, for elsewhere up to 10 days.
